metadata.inclusion:
A. Press Button switch 3 times in a row to link device to Z-Wave network or remove device from Z-Wave network. 
B. Press Button switch 3 times in a row again to cancel to link device to Z-Wave network.
metadata.exclusion:
A. Acknowledge of Green LED lightning. 
B. Press Button switch 3 times in a row to link device to Z-Wave network or remove device from Z-Wave network.
metadata.reset:
A. Press Fn switch over 2minutes to initialize connecting network information. 
Use this procedure only in the event that the network primary controller is missing or otherwise inoperable
